{"id":154,"date":"2025-02-02T16:29:52","date_gmt":"2025-02-02T13:29:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/?page_id=154"},"modified":"2025-03-18T18:57:33","modified_gmt":"2025-03-18T15:57:33","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"    <div class=\"top_section\">\r\n        <div class=\"top_container\">\r\n                        <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"top_elem elem_3\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/themes\/source\/images\/top_elem_3.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"top_info variable center\">\r\n                                                            <h1 class=\"title_page light blur_anim\">Our Story<\/h1>\r\n                                                        <\/div>\r\n                 \r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section\">\r\n        <div class=\"img_section\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_beige\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container p_100\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"container_inner\">\r\n                    <article class=\"about_article\">\r\n                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Source was founded in 2014 by Tom Jewell, a former Surrey cricketer with a family background in property. He began by helping fellow athletes navigate the complex property market, offering a streamlined service for sourcing, financing, and managing investments.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After assisting cricketer Chris Tremlett with his portfolio, Chris joined the company. Ollie Smith, with financial services experience, became Managing Director, enhancing the firm's expertise. Amber Choinski also came on board to lead the Lettings &amp; Management division.<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Source quickly expanded to support business owners and high-earning professionals facing similar time constraints. That same year, the company launched a nationwide lettings and management service, enabling clients to invest across multiple locations with a single point of contact.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The in-house management team provided both streamlined services and valuable data insights, giving Source a competitive edge.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>Since inception, Source has facilitated over \u00a3120 million in property investments across 25+ locations.<\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/article>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_light\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"description_section\">\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_section\">Meet our Team<\/h2>\r\n                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                        <p>A team of experts to help you with every aspect of building a successful property portfolio.<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"team_wrap\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Tom Jewell<\/span> <br>Founder<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Tom has a thirst for property knowledge and is a full member of the Association of Residential Lettings Agents. He founded the successful estate agency The Home Cloud in late 2014 and is an expert in helping investors maximise their property investment returns. His passion and expertise for investing is what has set him apart, and is one reason why Source\u2019s UK and Overseas client base is growing with such demand.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Ollie Smith<\/span> <br>Managing Director<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Ollie joined us in 2018 as a director. Prior to joining Source, he had a successful career working as a specialist foreign exchange broker in London. Ollie\u2019s role involves overseeing every aspect of the investment process and his background in financial services means he\u2019s well suited to advising new investors. He\u2019s also heavily involved in ensuring Source secures the best investment opportunities at the very best terms for our investors.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_3.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Chris Tremlett<\/span> <br>Non - Executive Director<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Chris began working as a director at Source early in 2015. He has years of property experience in development and long term investment and boasts an extensive portfolio of his own. Chris brings unique skills to Source, having previously played cricket professionally for England and Surrey before retiring from the game, he\u2019s passionate about helping sports men and women transition out of professional sport and plan for the future.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_4.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Amber Choinski<\/span> <br>Director of Lettings and Management<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Amber is our Operations Manager and has been with us since 2018. Her role puts her in charge of all aspects of purchase progression, letting and management of our fast growing nationwide portfolio of properties. Amber guides our clients through from reserving a property, legal progression and letting and management on completion of the purchase. She manages our in-house lettings team to ensure all tenancies are renewed quickly and efficiently, help keep void periods to an absolute minimum and manages properties to the highest standards.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_5.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Josh Bullen<\/span> <br>Head of Investment (UK)<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Josh has been working in the property sector since 2017. His expertise is in helping private investors build high-quality, diversified, long-term rental portfolios. He is especially adept at working with first-time investors at the start of their property investment journey. Josh also takes a leading role in our market research efforts at Source. He is becoming a valuable resource for our investors and the entire Source team with his in-depth research into market conditions, the mortgage market and new emerging investment hotspots.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Website-Headshot.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Sanyah Rashid <\/span> <br>Head of Sales <\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Sanyah joined Source in September 2024 and quickly took on the responsibility of managing the sales of both pre-tenanted and vacant properties, handling both off-market and on-market transactions. She provides weekly instructions, carries out daily valuations, and consistently brings exciting new properties to our exclusive database of private investors. Sanyah also works closely with the lettings &amp; management team, helping landlords sell their pre-tenanted properties. This ensures steady cash flow for landlords while minimizing disruption to tenants.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_6.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Em McCallum<\/span> <br>Marketing Manager<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Em joined in the summer of 2023 as our Marketing Executive. Her role includes strategizing and implementing our core marketing communications, such as email, website and paid media. Em also nurtures our brand identity, ensuring our brand evolves as we do, whilst keeping consistent with our values.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_7.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Evie Cleall<\/span> <br>Property Manager<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Once tenants are settled into the property, Evie manages any day-to-day maintenance issues that arise so that properties are repaired in an efficient manner. She also renews tenancies, ensuring rent prices increase in line with RPI rates to protect landlord yields. Evie frequently visits properties to make sure they are being maintained to a high standard and all property compliance documents are valid.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"team_item\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_img\">\r\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/team_8.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"team_item_info\">\r\n                                                        <p class=\"team_item_name\"><span>Izzy Kalloo<\/span> <br>Junior Lettings Coordinator<\/p>\r\n                                                        <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                <p>Izzy deals with all initial enquiries. She sees the tenancy process through from start to finish \u2013 organising viewings, negotiates tenancy offers and move-ins. In doing so, she ensures voids between tenancies are kept to a minimum.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_beige\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container p_120\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"container_inner\">\r\n                    <div class=\"testimonials_block\">\r\n                                                <h3 class=\"title_category\">See What Clients Say<\/h3>\r\n                                                <div class=\"testimonials_slider swiper swiper-container\">\r\n                            <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n                                                                <d